
 L T X                         clear_memories                     L T X
 
 NAME
	clear_memories - Clears memory patterns.

 SYNOPSIS
	clear_memories [<options>]

	The command clear_memories will clear the specified pattern 
	memories. There are four valid options:

		control	 - Control Pattern memory
		waveform - Waveform control memory
		data	 - Data pattern memory
		all	 - Control, waveform and data memory

